column5: Has anyone been up to Cranberry Portage lately and fished the Cranberry's, Simonhouse or Elbow? If so, what kind of success did you have? Plan on going up in about 3 weeks and wondering about any early successes. Thanks.

hey roscoe, i talked to a gut earlier who said he had good luck on elbow..go back in the message board to check it out. I am going up on the 17th of aug..let me know how you [email protected] good luck
